:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">带你感受最纯粹的快感</span></p><p begin="23.116" end="24.230" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="23.116" end="23.544">C.R.E.A.M.</span> <span begin="23.544" end="23.677">get</span> <span begin="23.677" end="23.897">the</span> <span begin="23.897" end="24.029">mo</span><span begin="24.029" end="24.230">ney</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">C.R.E.A.M. 拼命搞钱</span></p><p begin="23.866" end="26.362" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.866" end="23.947">Here</span> <span begin="23.947" end="24.178">we,</span> <span begin="24.178" end="24.332">here</span> <span begin="24.332" end="24.493">we</span> <span begin="24.493" end="24.803">go,</span> <span begin="24.873" end="25.171">check</span> <span begin="25.171" end="25.441">this</span> <span begin="25.441" end="25.721">shit,</span> <span begin="26.139" end="26.362">yo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">来了来了，听好这段</span></p><p begin="24.524" end="26.393" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="24.524" end="24.664">Dol</span><span begin="24.664" end="24.844">lar,</span> <span begin="24.844" end="24.992">dol</span><span begin="24.992" end="25.186">lar</span> <span begin="25.186" end="25.493">bill,</span> <span begin="25.493" end="26.393">y&apos;all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">钞票，钞票啊，兄弟们</span></p><p begin="26.627" end="29.526" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="26.627" end="26.781">I</span> <span begin="26.781" end="26.984">grew</span> <span begin="26.984" end="27.289">up</span> <span begin="27.289" end="27.437">on</span> <span begin="27.437" end="27.624">the</span> <span begin="27.624" end="27.980">crime</span> <span begin="27.980" end="28.331">side,</span> <span begin="28.331" end="28.457">the</span> <span begin="28.457" end="28.623">New</span> <span begin="28.623" end="28.955">York</span> <span begin="28.955" end="29.282">Times</span> <span begin="29.282" end="29.526">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我在犯罪街区长大，纽约街头的乱世里</span></p><p begin="29.815" end="31.254" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="29.815" end="29.963">Stay</span><span begin="29.963" end="30.132">in&apos;</span> <span begin="30.132" end="30.281">a</span><span begin="30.281" end="30.668">live</span> <span begin="30.668" end="30.791">was</span> <span begin="30.791" end="31.039">no</span> <span begin="31.039" end="31.254">jive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">活下去从不是儿戏</span></p><p begin="31.488" end="34.370" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="31.488" end="31.754">Had</span> <span begin="31.754" end="31.924">se</span><span begin="31.924" end="32.121">cond</span> <span begin="32.121" end="32.589">hands,</span> <span begin="32.807" end="33.136">Mom&apos;s</span> <span begin="33.136" end="33.430">bounced</span> <span begin="33.430" end="33.679">on</span> <span begin="33.679" end="33.962">old</span> <span begin="33.962" end="34.370">man</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">家里穷得叮当响，老妈离开了老爸</span></p><p begin="34.691" end="36.490" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="34.691" end="34.791">So</span> <span begin="34.791" end="34.949">then</span> <span begin="34.949" end="35.136">we</span> <span begin="35.136" end="35.451">moved</span> <span begin="35.451" end="35.629">to</span> <span begin="35.629" end="35.948">Shao</span><span begin="35.948" end="36.100">lin</span> <span begin="36.100" end="36.490">land</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">于是我们搬去了少林（斯塔滕岛）</span></p><p begin="36.690" end="39.709" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="36.690" end="36.781">A</span> <span begin="36.781" end="37.052">young</span> <span begin="37.052" end="37.398">youth,</span> <span begin="37.679" end="37.826">yo,</span> <span begin="37.826" end="38.049">ro</span><span begin="38.049" end="38.163">ckin&apos;</span> <span begin="38.163" end="38.311">the</span> <span begin="38.311" end="38.622">gold</span> <span begin="